      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$19,900 - Honest fair-condition car that still presents decently and offers a practical, budget-friendly option. It shows clear signs of age and use throughout, so it\u2019s not a perfect example, but it has been kept serviceable and can make a good fit for someone looking for solid transportation without spending big money.",
