    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Fair-condition vehicle being sold honestly as a used car with visible age and wear. Expect cosmetic blemishes around the exterior, some interior wear from regular use, and an overall presentation that is serviceable rather than especially clean or sharp. It should still be a workable vehicle for someone seeking basic transportation, but buyers should expect it to feel used and to likely want some maintenance or attention depending on their standards.",
      "price": 17900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean older vehicle in truly mint condition. It shows extremely well inside and out, with a very well-kept appearance, strong overall presentation, and the kind of condition that will stand out to buyers looking for a top-tier example rather than a project. This is not described as a fixer-upper or driver-quality car \u2014 it is the kind of vehicle a careful buyer can expect to be proud to own, with only the sort of minor age-related nuances you might look for on any older car. A very honest, high-end example for someone who wants one of the nicest ones available.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for buyers seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project at an accessible price point. It shows the signs of age and use you would expect, but it still presents a strong value for someone who prioritizes budget over perfection. If you're looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overcommitting, this is a compelling option worth a closer look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest old vehicle that could be a great fit for someone handy, in need of basic transportation, or after a solid project. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind and offers a chance to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you appreciate a straightforward sale and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a great opportunity.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Well-sorted driver with strong enthusiast appeal and solid mechanical character. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed with good road manners. Cosmetic wear and age-related blemishes are present, but this is a straightforward, usable car with a healthy powertrain foundation and plenty of upside for someone who wants an affordable platform to enjoy, improve, or build. Hard to find at this price point with this kind of drivability and potential.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap way into a car. Rough, used, and priced to move. Starts, drives, and gets the job done. Great beater, commuter, or project. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Honest, well-loved, and full of old-school character, this car is the kind of ride that still turns everyday errands into a little adventure. It has a lived-in charm and the kind of personality you just don\u2019t find in cookie-cutter commuters. A great fit for someone looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels, a weekend project, or a practical car with plenty of story left to tell.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with real value for the price. This vehicle is best suited for buyers seeking a practical project, backup car, or low-cost daily driver. It offers an accessible entry point into ownership and is being presented with clear, honest representation from a trusted seller. A smart buy for someone who recognizes opportunity and wants dependable value at a budget-friendly price.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    }
  ],
